  "text": "Immunohistochemical analyses of GLUT8 expression also proved its subcellular localization in human brain samples. Immunoreactivity of GLUT8 antibody was found in astrocytic and microglial cells in subependymal areas of human brains and also epithelial cells of the choroid plexus and ependymal cells [CITATION_1] .",
